{"tid":1893391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個生物膜技術口罩，可以即場殺死99.9%細菌？","createTime":"2020-02-23T08:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:11:32.000Z","uid":251110,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"accaff588d4dcddc1a7a33e200c095dc3936a9b5","tid":1893391,"uid":251110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"話說$100買咗3個BIO MASK，買之前睇過話可以殺死99.9%細菌，當中包括肺炎同sars。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0BTyyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0BTyyB.jpg&h=4344a9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfbgwmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdfbgwmg.jpg&h=b0c891f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFb搵到資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/706656289363422/posts/3196003657095327/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F706656289363422%2Fposts%2F3196003657095327%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=4d6fa9dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/706656289363422/posts/3196003657095327/?d=n</a><br />\n（&rdquo;Filligent-BioFriend BIO MASK&rdquo;與傳統N95口罩相比，BIO MASK的優勝點是更具透氣性、舒適度 (柔軟度)，生物膜技術使其配備殺菌功能，從而減低用家因身體與口罩表面接觸而導致交叉污染的風險。）<br />\n<br />\nMedgadget news：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.medgadget.com/2009/07/filligents_biomask_made_available_otc_in_asia.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medgadget.com%2F2009%2F07%2Ffilligents_biomask_made_available_otc_in_asia.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=2cfd1739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.medgadget.com/2009/07/filligents_biomask_made_available_otc_in_asia.html</a><br />\n（篇新聞稿大約係講：BioMask&trade;是Filligent Inc.稱為BioFriend的一系列產品的一部分，該產品使用的材料可現場殺死H1N1，MRSA，SARS和禽流感以及其他病原體。  BioFriend&trade;技術是一種可應用於各種基材的塗層，其工作原理是模仿人體細胞上的寡糖位點，病毒和細菌通常會通過這些位點附著。 更具體地說，該裝置模擬細胞膜表面寡糖上的末端唾液酸殘基。 一旦結合，病原體就會被嵌入的銅和鋅離子破壞，從而破壞其細胞壁並干擾其正常代謝。 這種方法的好處是，微生物被殺死而不是簡單地過濾。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦有網站宣稱呢隻口罩達到ASTM F2100-07 high barrier標準：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.medgadget.com/2011/06/biofriend-biomask-going-on-sale-in-u-s.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medgadget.com%2F2011%2F06%2Fbiofriend-biomask-going-on-sale-in-u-s.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=b5db9d2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.medgadget.com/2011/06/biofriend-biomask-going-on-sale-in-u-s.html</a><br />\n即PFE@0.1 micron 達98%，但官網上唔到無法confirm呢個說法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟喇..... 搭飛機應該戴呢個口罩好，定係戴返日本VPE BFE PFE 都99%嘅口罩呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b505c1084e9c805611f0c92ea0d2abccf9677e0a","tid":1893391,"uid":66559,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"病毒同細菌都未搞清楚"},{"pid":"49aa8fa770fed562c83b18dcf142d9ddf73dd32b","tid":1893391,"uid":121058,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"個簡介細菌同病毒都未分清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7d79e68d5bbc11fbe91cf910fe2c4832ceab21","tid":1893391,"uid":25635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"今年若具爾獎仲唔係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19aa73cac57e2a8a5c4c703c723613c6f26975d7","tid":1893391,"uid":4330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"英文有寫virus"},{"pid":"74e1fe031b8d86091504671875f542399dc09801","tid":1893391,"uid":251110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19aa73cac57e2a8a5c4c703c723613c6f26975d7","tid":1893391,"uid":4330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:4